---
---

<section id="about" class="py-24 md:py-32 px-6 relative">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
    <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row gap-12 lg:gap-20 items-center">
      
      <!-- Premium Terminal Card -->
      <div class="reveal-left w-full lg:w-5/12 aspect-[4/5] glass-panel rounded-2xl flex flex-col relative overflow-hidden group shadow-2xl shadow-black/40">
        <!-- Terminal Header (macOS style) -->
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-3 bg-slate-800/80 backdrop-blur-md border-b border-white/[0.04]">
          <div class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-[#ff5f56] border border-black/10"></div>
          <div class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-[#ffbd2e] border border-black/10"></div>
          <div class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-[#27c93f] border border-black/10"></div>
          <div class="flex-1 flex justify-center">
            <span class="font-mono text-[10px] text-slate-400 font-medium tracking-wide">youssef@fedora: ~</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Terminal Content -->
        <div class="font-mono text-sm leading-8 flex-1 overflow-hidden p-5 md:p-6 bg-slate-900/50">
          <div class="mb-4">
            <span class="text-primary font-bold">❯</span>
            <span class="text-slate-300"> whoami</span>
            <br/>
            <span class="text-white pl-4">Youssef Ashraf</span>
          </div>

          <div class="mb-4">
            <span class="text-primary font-bold">❯</span>
            <span class="text-slate-300"> cat role.txt</span>
            <br/>
            <span class="text-blue-400 pl-4 font-medium">Data Engineering Trainee</span>
          </div>

          <div class="mb-4">
            <span class="text-primary font-bold">❯</span>
            <span class="text-slate-300"> cat education.txt</span>
            <br/>
            <span class="text-slate-300 pl-4">CS @ NUB — Class of 2028</span>
          </div>

          <div class="mb-4 items-center">
            <span class="text-primary font-bold">❯</span>
            <span class="text-slate-300"> uname -a</span>
            <br/>
            <span class="text-slate-300 pl-4">Fedora Linux</span>
          </div>

          <div class="mb-4">
            <span class="text-primary font-bold">❯</span>
            <span class="text-slate-300"> cat interests.txt</span>
            <br/>
            <span class="text-accent pl-4">["AI", "Systems", "Hardware"]</span>
          </div>

          <div>
            <span class="text-primary font-bold animate-pulse">_</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Premium hover glow -->
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-tr from-primary/5 via-transparent to-accent/5 opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-700 pointer-events-none"></div>
      </div>

      <!-- Bio Content -->
      <div class="reveal-right w-full lg:w-7/12">
        <h2 class="section-heading">
          <span class="font-mono text-primary text-sm tracking-wider uppercase">01. About Me</span>
          <span class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold bg-clip-text text-transparent bg-gradient-to-r from-white to-slate-400">
            The Person Behind the Code
          </span>
        </h2>

        <div class="space-y-5 text-slate-400 leading-relaxed text-base md:text-lg font-light">
          <p>
            I'm <span class="text-white font-medium">Youssef Ashraf</span>, a Computer Science 
            undergraduate at Nahda University (Class of 2028) and a Data Engineering Trainee at the 
            <span class="text-primary font-medium">Digital Egypt Pioneers Initiative (DEPI)</span>.
          </p>
          
          <p>
            Unlike typical developers, I thrive at the intersection of 
            <span class="text-white">Software</span> and 
            <span class="text-white">Hardware</span>. 
            My journey started with building Embedded Systems projects using Arduino and C++, 
            which naturally evolved into a passion for Linux and System Administration.
          </p>

          <p>
            Whether I'm customizing my Fedora kernel, wiring an Arduino robot, or building 
            a data pipeline in Python — I am driven by a curiosity to understand how things 
            work <span class="font-mono text-primary/80 bg-primary/10 px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded text-sm">under_the_hood</span>.
          </p>

          <!-- Current Focus (Redesigned as premium list) -->
          <div class="mt-8 pt-8 border-t border-slate-800">
            <p class="font-mono text-xs text-slate-500 mb-4 uppercase tracking-widest">// Current Focus</p>
            <ul class="space-y-3">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <div class="mt-1 w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-primary/70 shadow-[0_0_8px_rgba(56,189,248,0.6)]"></div>
                <span class="text-slate-300">Building intelligent, hardware-integrated software solutions</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <div class="mt-1 w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-blue-400/70 shadow-[0_0_8px_rgba(96,165,250,0.6)]"></div>
                <span class="text-slate-300">Learning Advanced Deep Learning (CNNs) & Model Optimization</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <div class="mt-1 w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-accent/70 shadow-[0_0_8px_rgba(139,92,246,0.6)]"></div>
                <span class="text-slate-300">Designing AI & Data Science roadmaps for the community</span>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
